{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/GloomveilGif01.gif?t=1736110546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>A journey to uncover the hidden kingdom of Gloomveil, a once-flourishing land of sentient insects now shrouded in the shadows of the forest.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/LineTest.png?t=1736110546\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/Banner_01.png?t=1736110546\" />Explore a <strong>vast</strong>, <strong>interconnected </strong>world that doesn't revolve around you. Each corner hides <strong>secrets </strong>waiting to be uncovered. Create <strong>shortcuts </strong>and familiarize yourself with the land to stay on course</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/Banner_02.png?t=1736110546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Gloomveil, <strong>navigating </strong>the world isn't just a means to an end\u2014it's the <strong>essence of the gameplay</strong>. Observe the creatures around you and move through their territory with <strong>caution</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/Banner_03.png?t=1736110546\" />Sometimes, in moments of <strong>haste </strong>or <strong>fear</strong>, you might feel compelled to use your <strong>weapon</strong>. It\u2019s your <strong>choice</strong>, but be aware that this could lead to<strong> unforeseen consequences</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/LineTest.png?t=1736110546\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/GloomveilGif04.gif?t=1736110546\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Local Co-op</strong>: Play with friends in local cooperative mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Vertical and Horizontal Exploration</strong>: Navigate through a world designed for both vertical and horizontal exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Dynamic Day-Night Cycle</strong>: Experience a day-night cycle with events that change based on the time of day.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Flexible Playstyles</strong>: Complete the game using any playstyle\u2014every approach is viable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Accessible Controls</strong>: Play with one hand, using keyboard-only, mouse-only, or either side of the gamepad.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Offer Help to Creatures</strong>: Lend a helping hand to creatures you encounter along the way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Environmental Storytelling</strong>: Immerse yourself in a world where the environment tells its own story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Optional Dialogues</strong>: Engage in dialogues only if you choose\u2014perfect for players who prefer action over conversation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Minimal UI</strong>: Enjoy a clean, immersive experience with minimal UI and no distracting indicators.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156020/extras/GloomveilGif08.gif?t=1736110546\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstat